<h3 class="auk-h3">Arguments (DropdownMenu)</h3>

<div class="auk-u-mb-4">
  <p>Wether <span class="auk-u-text-code">button</span> or <span class="auk-u-text-code">button-link</span> is defined as <span class="auk-u-text-code">@type</span>, it will be possible to pass the same arguments as the corresponding component. See <LinkTo @route="styleguide.button-skins">Button (skins)</LinkTo>, <LinkTo @route="styleguide.button-types">Button (types)</LinkTo> or <LinkTo @route="styleguide.link-button">Buttons (link)</LinkTo> for all references. If such an argument is defined in the table below anyways, it has a default added to it (within this component).</p>
</div>

<table class="auk-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Argument</th>
      <th>Type</th>
      <th>Possible values</th>
      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td><code>@type</code></td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td class="auk-table__col--3"><code>button</code> (default) or <code>button-link</code></td>
      <td>Determines wether the initiator is rendered as <code>Button</code> or <code>ButtonLink</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>@layout</code></td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td class="auk-table__col--3"><code>icon-only</code>, <code>icon-left</code> or <code>icon-right</code> (default)</td>
      <td>Determines the layout of the initiator. The layout is automatically determined from the presence of <code>@label</code>, unless <code>icon-only</code> is specified this will result in a button layout with icon on the right.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>@icon</code></td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td class="auk-table__col--3">Name of the icon, see <LinkTo @route="styleguide.icons">Icons</LinkTo> for all references.</td>
      <td>Determines the icon used within the initiator. Defaults to <code>chevron-down</code> if <code>@layout</code> starts with <code>right-</code>, <code>bottom-</code> & <code>left-</code> or <code>chevron-up</code> if it starts with <code>top-</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><code>@placement</code></td>
      <td>string</td>
      <td class="auk-table__col--3"><code>top</code>, <code>top-start</code>, <code>top-end</code>, <code>right</code>, <code>right-start</code>, <code>right-end</code>, <code>bottom</code>, <code>bottom-start</code>, <code>bottom-end</code> (default), <code>left</code>, <code>left-start</code>, <code>left-end</code></td>
      <td>Determines position of the menu against the initiator.</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

